data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. With its beautiful design and ideal layout, this house is a dream come true. The new roof, installed this year, ensures worry-free living for years to come. Inside you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light that flows effortlessly throughout the home, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The spacious kitchen is a true highlight, featuring granite countertops, dark cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. On the main floor, you'll find a convenient office, complete with elegant French doors. All 4 bedrooms are housed upstairs for added privacy. The primary suite boasts its own private ensuite, equipped with a double vanity, a luxurious tub, and a separate shower. Outside, the fenced backyard provides a safe and secure area for outdoor activities. The community offers an array of fantastic amenities, including ponds, a fitness center, a dog park, and a refreshing pool – ideal for enjoying summertime to the fullest.
